    "causal_summary": "Two peck research passes inform this packet. The 2026-06-02 README analysis (child phase 001) found four philosophy-neutral mechanisms (T1-T4); the research/006 source-mining pass (cross-model verified) found a further set in peck's agent prompts and benchmark harness (T5-T10) and produced a concrete, now-adoptable design for the T1 coverage gate that the README pass had deferred. All of these adopt peck mechanisms into the same spec-kit verification/quality surfaces, so they belong in one phase-parent that sequences them without duplicating implementation detail.",
